Class DriverUtil

java.lang.Object
driverutility.DriverUtil
public class DriverUtil extends Object
DriverUtil class provides utility methods to manage WebDriver instances, launch applications, and handle browser windows. It uses ThreadLocal to ensure that each thread has its own instance of WebDriver.
Since:
2025-05-30
Version:
